description: Some exemplary trajectories of European Herring Gulls (Larus argentatus Pontoppidan, 1736) and Lesser Black-backed Gulls (Larus fuscus Linnaeus, 1758), tracked with the LifeWatch bird tracking GPS network. Displayed positions are calculated centroid positions of daily tracks.
keywords: bird, GPS tracking, migration patterns, habitat use, Species distribution
name: Trajectory European herring gull (Hilde, Belgium, 2016)
